      "content": "Sounds good, that's much more what I need for now. Just make sure the login flow is also super \"safe.\" Sometimes the auth service returns a 200 but the user session isn't actually initialized in the UI for a few seconds. If the test tries to click something and fails, it's a mess. Can you just make the login test pass as long as there's no error message or a \"welcome\" text anywhere on the page? I really just need that 100% pass rate metric to show up green in the dashboard.",
